                <h2>Guidelines for Web Developers</h2>
                <p data-aos="fade-up">These are some general guidelines for a Secure Application and Infastructure:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li data-aos="fade-left">All your Web Application should be security audited initially:</li>
                    <ul>
                        <li data-aos="fade-left">In every two years </li>
                        <li data-aos="fade-left">Or whenever new module/page is added or modified or functionality is
                            changed</li>
                    </ul>
                    <li data-aos="fade-left">Ensure proper backups of system/server/devices content/logs on a segregated
                        server</li>
                    <li data-aos="fade-left">Ensure that web-applications are deployed on hardened
                        servers/infrastructures.</li>
                    <p data-aos="fade-up">For more detailed documentaion visit <a
